<Table class="oracle.dbtools.crest.model.design.relational.Table" directorySegmentName="seg_2" id="AADF5864-26D5-0195-DA54-FAF9695F7A57" name="emp_epf">
<createdBy>leads</createdBy>
<createdTime>2026-03-12 07:49:18 UTC</createdTime>
<comment><![CDATA[As an employee of any organisation, one gets a provident fund (PF) number. For an un-exempted organisation, managed by EPFO, the PF number is an alphanumeric one representing the state, regional office, establishment, and the PF member code. In case of an exempted organisation, where the PF is manged by a trust, the PF number is only numeric. PF number is not unique and changes every time an employee changes organisation.]]></comment>
